just a commercial. It’s a celebration of ambition—a cinematic tribute to every dream fueled by motion, sweat, and belief.\n\n🔧 Tools Used:\n\nAI Imagery: Midjourney, Flux, Veo Imagen 3\n\nVideo: Veo 2, Kling AI 2.0\n\nMusic: Suno AI\n\nVoice: Elevenlabs\n\nConcept, Script, Direction \u0026 Editing: 100% Human\n\n🔥 This project explores how AI can amplify the raw energy of human ambition, when guided by real passion and purpose. Nike didn’t make this film. But their story—and our dreams—did.\n\n👉 AI is not the athlete. We are.\n\n#Nike #AITools #AICommercial #AthleteSpirit #EmotionalAI #SunoAI #ElevenLabs #Veo2 #Midjourney #AIFilmmaking #GenerativeAI #DreamBig #klingai \n‪@Kling_ai‬ ‪@googledeepmind‬ ‪@elevenlabsio‬","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":840,"length":5,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CCYQ3NcEGCMiEwi73520ovKTAxX_UTgFHbvKMZXKAQTwWj1V","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"/hashtag/nike","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_BROWSE","rootVe":6827,"apiUrl":"/youtubei/v1/browse"}},"browseEndpoint":{"browseId":"FEhashtag","params":"6gUICgRuaWtlGAE%3D"}}},"loggingDirectives":{"trackingParams":"CCYQ3NcEGCMiEwi73520ovKTAxX_UTgFHbvKMZU="}},{"startIndex":846,"length":8,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CCUQ3NcEGCQiEwi73520ovKTAxX_UTgFHbvKMZXKAQTwWj1V","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"/hashtag/aitools","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_BROWSE","rootVe":6827,"apiUrl":"/youtubei/v1/browse"}},"browseEndpoint":{"browseId":"FEhashtag","params":"6gULCgdhaXRvb2xzGAE%3D"}}},"loggingDirectives":{"trackingParams":"CCUQ3NcEGCQiEwi73520ovKTAxX_UTgFHbvKMZU="}},{"startIndex":855,"length":13,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CCQQ3NcEGCUiEwi73520ovKTAxX_UTgFHbvKMZXKAQTwWj1V","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"/hashtag/aicommercial","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_BROWSE","rootVe":6827,"apiUrl":"/youtubei/v1/browse"}},"browseEndpoint":{"browseId":"FEhashtag","params":"6gUQCgxhaWNvbW1lcmNpYWwYAQ%3D%3D"}}},"loggin